   3: ## Fixed
   4: - **[P0] Missing await on response.json()** (line ~17) â€” `response.json()` returns a Promise; without `await`, `setItems` receives a Promise object instead of data. Fixed: added `await`.
   5: - **[P1] No error handling in fetchItems** (line ~15) â€” Network errors crash silently, `loading` stays true forever. Fixed: added try/catch/finally.
   6: - **[P1] No error handling in deleteItem** (line ~23) â€” Failed DELETE removes item from UI optimistically with no rollback. Fixed: added try/catch, check `res.ok`.
