   8: - **[P1] Hardcoded user-facing strings** (lines 36,40,44) â€” No i18n. Fixed: added useI18n, replaced with t() keys.
   9: - **[P1] Stale closure in deleteItem** (line 30) â€” `setItems(items.filter(...))` loses concurrent deletes. Fixed: functional updater `setItems(prev => ...)`.
  10: - **[P1] No response.ok check in fetchItems** (line 17) â€” Non-2xx responses treated as success. Fixed: added `if (!response.ok) throw`.
  11: - **[P2] Inline styles instead of Tailwind** (line 39) â€” `style={{ padding: 16 }}`. Fixed: replaced with `className="p-4"`.
  12: - **[P2] console.error in production** (lines 20,32) â€” No user feedback. Fixed: removed console.error, added error state display.
  13: - **[P2] No minimum touch target for Delete** (line 44) â€” Below 44x44px. Fixed: added min-h/min-w classes.
  14: - **[P2] No empty state** â€” Empty items shows nothing. Fixed: added empty state message.
  15: - **[P2] No user-facing error feedback** â€” Errors only in console. Fixed: added error state and UI display.
  16: 
  17: - **[P1] Hardcoded error strings** (lines 20,33) â€” "Fetch failed"/"Delete failed" not using i18n. Fixed: replaced with `t('test_page.fetch_failed')` / `t('test_page.delete_failed')`.
  18: - **[P2] No loading/disabled state on Delete button** (lines 50-55) â€” Double-click causes duplicate DELETEs. Fixed: added `deletingId` state, disabled button during delete.
  19: - **[P2] Error state never cleared on success** (lines 24,36) â€” Stale error persists after successful actions. Fixed: added `setError(null)` at start of fetchItems and deleteItem.
  20: - **[P2] List items lack flex layout** (line 48) â€” Name and button stack vertically on mobile. Fixed: added `flex items-center justify-between` to item div.
